### {203}{}{Too kind to be true. My name is Abel, I am one of the Followers of Fire, if that means anything to you. Now stop wasting my time.}
{203}{}{太善良了，不可能是真的。我的名字叫亚伯，我是火的追随者之一，如果这对你有什么意义的话。现在别再浪费我的时间了。 -- Too kind to be true. My name is Abel, I am one of the Followers of Fire, if that means anything to you. Now stop wasting my time.}
